  <entry>
    <title>关于Tangyuxian主题对文章无法正常检测分类和标签的解决方案</title>
    <link href="http://chenglan29.github.io/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8ETangyuxian%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/"/>
    <id>http://chenglan29.github.io/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8ETangyuxian%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</id>
    <published>2026-02-04T16:34:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-02-04T16:46:32.008Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我发现这个主题 hexo server 启动时不会自动检测文章的分类和标签，</p><p>但是可以在 hexo server 启动之后，<br>并且在 hexo generate –watch 监视之后对文章进行修改<br>便可以解决问题</p><p>于是我写出了一下代码(笑哭)</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> fs = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">&quot;fs&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">fs.<span class="title function_">readdirSync</span>(<span class="string">&quot;./source/_posts&quot;</span>).<span class="title function_">forEach</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">item</span>=&gt;</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> name = <span class="string">&quot;./source/_posts/&quot;</span>+item;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> inner = fs.<span class="title function_">readFileSync</span>(<span class="string">&quot;./source/_posts/&quot;</span>+item).<span class="title function_">toString</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    fs.<span class="title function_">writeFileSync</span>(name,inner+<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    fs.<span class="title function_">writeFileSync</span>(name,inner.<span class="title function_">substr</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,inner.<span class="property">length</span>));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;我发现这个主题 hexo server 启动时不会自动检测文章的分类和标签，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是可以在 hexo server 启动之后，&lt;br&gt;并且在 hexo generate –watch 监视之后对文章进行修改&lt;br&gt;便可以解决问题&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;于是我写出了一下代</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>显示最近的实体</title>
